{"word":"Measure","slug":"measure","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Measure</b> Dry:<br/> - 1. Bushel, about a peck<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=5&verse=15'>Mat 5:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=4&verse=21'>Mar 4:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=11&verse=33'>Luk 11:33</a> <br/> - 2. Cab, or kab, about two quarts<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=6&verse=25'>2Ki 6:25</a> <br/> - 3. Cor, equal to one homer or ten ephahs, equal to about eleven and one-ninth bushels<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=22'>1Ki 4:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=5&verse=11'>1Ki 5:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=2&verse=10'>2Ch 2:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=27&verse=5'>2Ch 27:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=7&verse=22'>Ezr 7:22</a> <br/> - 4. Ephah, equal to three seah, and in liquid, to a bath, containing about a bushel and a half<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=16&verse=36'>Exo 16:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=5&verse=11'>Lev 5:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=6&verse=20'>Lev 6:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=19&verse=36'>Lev 19:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=5&verse=15'>Num 5:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=28&verse=5'>Num 28:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=6&verse=19'>Jdg 6:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=2&verse=17'>Rth 2:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=1&verse=24'>1Sa 1:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=17&verse=17'>1Sa 17:17</a>; <a hre