ofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=26'>1Ki 7:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=38'>1Ki 7:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=2&verse=10'>2Ch 2:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=4&verse=5'>2Ch 4:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=7&verse=22'>Ezr 7:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=5&verse=10'>Isa 5:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=45&verse=11'>Eze 45:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=45&verse=14'>Eze 45:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=16&verse=6'>Luk 16:6</a> <br/> - 2. Firkin, nearly nine gallons<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=2&verse=6'>Joh 2:6</a> <br/> - 3. Hin, about a gallon and a half<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=40'>Exo 29:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=24'>Exo 30:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=19&verse=36'>Lev 19:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=23&verse=13'>Lev 23:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=15&verse=10'>Num 15:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=28&verse=5'>Num 28:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=28&verse=7'>Num 28:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=28&verse=14'>Num 28:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=4&verse=11'>Eze 4:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=45&verse=24'>Eze 45:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=46&verse=5'>Eze 46:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=46&verse=7'>Eze 46:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=46&verse=11'>Eze 46:11</